    "dashboard.energy.breakdown" : {
      "comment" : "Energy card subtitle splitting today's total into active vs. basal calories. Format args: %1$lld = active kcal (Int), %2$lld = basal/resting kcal (Int). Keep both placeholders; reorder positionally if the target language requires it (was: 活动 %d · 静息 %d).",
